data.description: Opportunity awaits! Welcome to this 2 bed 1 bath ranch style home in the desirable section of Palmyra! This home has been lovingly cared for by the original owners and is ready for you to make it your own! The living room is a large space, offering a bay window creating natural light, recessed lighting, has carpet, ceiling fan and a large coat closet. The living room flows into the dining room and kitchen area, great for entertaining. The kitchen has plenty of cabinets, making the most of this space! There is a newer stainless steel refrigerator. There are 2 bedrooms (originally 3 but owners converted the 3rd into one master bedroom). The main bedroom offers 2 large closets and 2 ceiling fans. The 2nd bedroom is currently used as a laundry area, but laundry hook ups are also in the basement, so can easily be converted back to a regular bedroom.  The basement is full size. Half has been finished with paneling and carpet.  The fenced in backyard can be your very own oasis!  There is an in ground pool with a liner (which has been replaced within the last 5 years) and you'll have endless fun with the slide into the 8 ft deep end! There is a large maintenance free trex deck that is great to relax and enjoy the yard.  There is a large shed for storage. You'll love the solar panels to help off set the cost of gas and electricity.  This is a great opportunity to own a home in a wonderful neighborhood . This home is being sold in its as-is condition, buyer responsible for twp CO and any repairs needed to obtain a mortgage. Join us at the Open House Sunday, Feb 25th.
